description:
In "Chickempic," the multiplayer mode of Viviter where you can play with up to 8 players, we're adding the "Chicken Ranger" mini-game!
That monster is causing havoc as it pleases.
Alright, it's my time to shine!
Here comes the Rider of Justice, ViviterV3!!
Your mischief ends here, monster! I'll defeat you with my kick!!
Gathering my strength... Here I go! Take this! Haaaaaaa!!!!
name: Additional mini-game "Chicken Ranger"
